enzos de la Edad Moderna. ‹br/›Varios estudios se centran en grandes relatos de la tradición bíblica (el rey David, la vida del glorioso patriarca San José) y otros analizan en detalle algunas historias del inmenso caudal hagiográfico (San Isidro, San Ignacio, San Frutos).‹br/›El tomo ofrece la primera aportación monográfica dedicada en exclusiva al ‹i›epos‹/i› sacro, una materia apasionante que aguarda todavía un rescate editorial y crítico.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aEpic poetry, SpanishyClassical period, 1500-1700xCriticism and interpretation. 0aReligion in literatureyClassical period, 1500-1700. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / Spanish & Portuguese.2bisacsh1 aArellano, Ignacio, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBlanco, Mercedes, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCano Gómez, Guillermo José, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChoi, Imogen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFadón Duarte, Alberto, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPonce Cárdenas, Jesús, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPonce Cárdenas, Jesús, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aStein, Tadeo Pablo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertVervuert Complete eBook-Package 2023z9783110998719oZDB-207-IBV40uhttps://doi.org/10.31819/978396869479540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783968694795423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783968694795/original  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-207-IBVb2023